<template>
      <el-table :columns="columns" :data="tableData" style="width: 100%">
           <el-table-column v-for="item in columns" :prop="item.prop" :label="item.name" :key="item.prop" >
              <template #default="scope">
                     <slot :name="item.slotname">{{scope.row[scope.item.prop]}}</slot>
              </template>
           </el-table-column>
     </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name:"myTable",
  props:{
    tableData:{
        type:Array,
        default:()=>{
        }
    },
    columns:{
        type:Array,
        default:()=>{
        }
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
